column3: I say this because it’s ace and made me want to go for a ride but it should be longer!
Nice video but the jerseys are not for me.
So did they get a KOM?

Love it! But I must say, if you're going to go through all the trouble and energy to make a short film, you might want to make it more than 48 seconds long. Just sayin', a few minutes long would have been perfect.
One of your best. There where some really nice transitions in this edit and a great pace throughout.
